channel.title: AMD or INTEL
channel.description:
Hey, right now im contemplating a compleate swap-over and joining the dark side of the force. I.E. Converting my pc from intel and getting a amd box. no-matter what, im going to upgrade my pc, but what i want to know is if i should to this "conversion", Atm i have $600 (NZD) and thats enough to get the amd stuff now, or save up another 200 for the intel box... These are my two choices:
Plan A the amd upgrade: [url=http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=261/ID=14206/SID=1014520548/productdetails.html] http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=261/ID=14206/SID=1014520548/productdetails.html[/url] [url=http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=188/ID=2852/SID=160342863/productdetails.html]http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=188/ID=2852/SID=160342863/productdetails.html[/url] and[url=http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=254/ID=6682/SID=1051025654/productdetails.html] http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=254/ID=6682/SID=1051025654/productdetails.html[/url]
OR Plan B The intel upgrade
[url=http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=375/ID=9845/SID=1059132209/productdetails.html]http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=375/ID=9845/SID=1059132209/productdetails.html[/url]
[url=http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=474/ID=13763/SID=15104834/productdetails.html]http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=474/ID=13763/SID=15104834/productdetails.html[/url]
And [url=http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=254/ID=6682/SID=1051025654/productdetails.html] http://www.playtech.co.nz/afawcs0139235/CATID=254/ID=6682/SID=1051025654/productdetails.html[/url]
the amd upgrade will cost around 600, the intel upgrade, around 750-800 (Its in NZD) but yeah, i would like to hear your oppinions on this.
